data.description: Brick Front End Unit, 3 level, 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom townhome located in the sought after subdivision of Oxford Landing! In the beautiful capital city of Maryland, Annapolis! NEWER ROOF with warranty that transfers, NEWER A/C Unit ,and hot water heater! Boasting a spacious floor plan including a separate living room, dining room, eat in kitchen area, and family room off of the kitchen. Retreat to your huge owner’s suite which offers vaulted ceilings, large closet space, a separate soaking tub and shower, and skylights which allows natural light and charm in the bathroom. The fully finished basement offers a fireplace and a full bathroom. Entertain guest and enjoy nice weather on the deck! Take in all that Annapolis has to offer from its rich history and museum without walls to the local shopping malls, farmers markets, and eateries. This quaint city, tucked away off of the Chesapeake Bay is surrounded by waterways that offer water taxis, tours of the city, water front dining and beaches. Near downtown Annapolis, the Naval Academy, RT. 50, the Bay Bridge, and an easy commute to DC and Baltimore. Make this house your home today! Sold As-Is
